detailIntroText: Age of Dino (AOD) is a next-generation Massively Multiplayer Online (MMO) strategy game built on the Xterio Foundation platform. Set within an enthraling metaverse, AOD offers a captivating journey that encompasses both SLG (SimulationGame) and RPG (Role-Playing Game) elements. The gaming experience includes feeding dinosaurs, resourcecollection, adventures, park building, and epic battles against Al-controlled adversaries and armies ofmutant dinosaurs.
